# CDMX

> CDMX is a premium one-person B2B growth consultancy based in Bruges, Belgium, founded by Renke Pieters. Retainer-only, one client at a time. Investment starts at €5K/month with a 1-year engagement.

## What CDMX Does
CDMX embeds a single operator across three disciplines — digital growth, business strategy, and AI & automation — inside one B2B client at a time. This is not advisory work. The operator builds, ships, and iterates alongside the client's team.

## Services
- Digital Growth: Growth architecture, attribution, channel strategy, structured experimentation
- Business Strategy: Business model clarity, execution planning, growth forecasting, board-ready deliverables
- AI & Automation: Production-grade AI systems built into operations — not slide decks or pilots

## Target Audience
- B2B companies with 20-200 employees
- Companies at a growth inflection point
- Based in Belgium or across Europe
- Looking for senior capacity without three separate hires

## Track Record
- EUR 1M+ revenue generated through new sales channels (Belgian full-service marketing agency, 2024-2026)
- 5 AI products shipped to production
- Audit review cycles cut by 3x
- 18-month embedded engagement in a 50+ person marketing agency

## Engagement Model
- Retainer-only, one client at a time
- 1-year initial commitment
- Investment starts at EUR 5K/month — less than a single senior hire, across three domains
- Application-based intake process with 48-hour response

